{"type":null,"faqId":46348,"title":"Huawei Watch_What do I need to pay attention to when using the stainless steel mesh strap?","answer":"<a name=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757385\"></a><a name=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757385\"></a><div id=\"body1442371814964\"><ol id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757385__ol9539618174834\"><li id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757385__li18747699174834\">Keep the strap level when inserting it into the clasp.<p id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757385__p2142748717498\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7345e_djiyu.png\"></span></p></li><li id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757385__li18559933174917\">Ensure that the metallic protrusive part on the clasp remains within the adjustable area marked on the strap.<p id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757385__p56062178174928\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7345f_kvpxd.png\"></span></p><div class=\"note\" id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757385__note63028544174956\"><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/73460_iavcj.gif\"><span class=\"notetitle\"> NOTE: </span><div class=\"notebody\"><ul id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757385__ul59639855174958\"><li id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757385__li66996653174958\">Do not attempt to secure the clasp outside of the adjustable area. This may cause irreparable damage to your strap.</li><li id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757385__li66098968174958\">If it feels like you need to use force to secure the clasp, adjust the strap slightly and then try again.</li></ul></div></div></li></ol></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div>","faqTypeId":591,"faqType":"Product Maintenance","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":1,"languageName":"en","faqCode":"en-us_topic_0019757385","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Product-Maintenance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444636924000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":53,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"stainless, steel,mesh, strap, attention","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}